Which transitaire in New Caledonia has the most clients?
Begin!

The task is to find out which transitaire (freight forwarder) in New Caledonia has the most clients. However, the tools provided are related to SQUAKE, which helps businesses calculate carbon emissions and purchase climate contributions. These tools do not directly provide information about transitaires or their client counts.

Since I do not have access to tools that can directly answer this question, I will need to give up and restart.
